# Data Directory

This directory stores client data and outreach history.

Each client gets their own subdirectory with:
- `prospects.json` - All prospect data and generated outreach
- `company_insights.json` - Reusable company insights

## Structure

```
data/
└── {client_id}/
    ├── prospects.json
    └── company_insights.json
```

Client directories are created automatically when you run the application.
